name: Drifting Remains 1.1
description:
An audio-reactive, generative adversarial network trained on over 1000 photos of tree skin and bones washed ashore on Vancouver Island. Cutoff or plucked from their roots, these drifting sun-bleached spines shed their skin to find land once again. Salty ghosts' laid bare in their final destination. (Sound On)

3072 x 1024 pixels | Ryan Thompson, September 2021 | www.ryanthompson.name
